# Project Learning Log

- Treat the root `README.md` as the project journal and learning log.
- When adding a new UI feature, update the `Milestones`, `UI Concepts Learned`, or `Current Feature Summary` section.
- Keep updates short and practical: one row or bullet per feature/concept.
- Record concepts the user is learning, such as React hooks, controlled inputs, routing, API calls, Tailwind patterns, pagination, sorting, or reusable components.
- Do not duplicate long explanations from code comments; summarize what was learned and where it appears in the project.
